=begin pod
=TITLE Gnome::Gtk4::R-PrintOperationPreview
=head1 Description

L<Gnome::Gtk4::R-PrintOperationPreview|/content-docs/api2/reference/Gtk4/R-PrintOperationPreview> is the interface that is used to
implement print preview.

A L<Gnome::Gtk4::R-PrintOperationPreview|/content-docs/api2/reference/Gtk4/R-PrintOperationPreview> object is passed to the
I<preview defined in PrintOperation> signal by
L<Gnome::Gtk4::PrintOperation|/content-docs/api2/reference/Gtk4/PrintOperation>.

